## Containment Actions Taken

1. Isolated all encrypted hosts at the network switch level (VLAN quarantine)
2. Disabled domain account `svc_backup2` and reset `jmartin` credentials
3. Revoked all active VPN sessions and patched CVE-2023-46805
4. Blocked IOC hashes in CrowdStrike Custom IOC policy
5. Engaged MEGA legal team for exfiltration data preservation request
6. Initiated AD forest recovery procedure from clean offline backup (D-7)

